               <item n="m_philcomment_old">&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;a1.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;ane waṣtaṃtu&lt;/i&gt; glosses Skt. &lt;i&gt;śayanā&lt;/i&gt; 'Lagerstätten' ['storage facilities'] ([[Waldschmidt 1968]]: 108); &lt;i&gt;sakkāk&lt;/i&gt; glosses Skt. &lt;i&gt;karṇaprāsādāḥ&lt;/i&gt; (nom.pl.) 'Ausbau; Erker (?)' ['extension; gazebo (?)'] ([[SWTF]]: II, 25b; [[Waldschmidt 1968]]: 108, 'Ausbauten' ['extensions']).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;a4.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;ets&lt;/i&gt; glosses Skt. &lt;i&gt;irṣyāko&lt;/i&gt; (for &lt;i&gt;īrṣyako&lt;/i&gt;) 'jealous' (cf. [[Waldschmidt 1968]]: 109, 'eifersüchtig'); &lt;i&gt;yisli&lt;/i&gt; glosses Skt. &lt;i&gt;matsarī&lt;/i&gt; 'envious, jealous' (cf. [[Waldschmidt 1968]]: 109, 'neidisch').&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;a5&lt;/b&gt; glosses Skt. &lt;i&gt;badhnata&lt;/i&gt; (2pl.ipv.; for &lt;i&gt;badhnīta&lt;/i&gt;, see [[Waldschmidt 1968]]: 109) 'bind!'.&lt;/p&gt;</item>
